<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,minimum-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no" />
    <title>长沙辰才一对一志愿填报指导</title>
    <meta name="keywords" content="">
    <meta name="description" content="">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="favicon.ico">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/reset.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/xuanke.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="publicHead"></div>
    <div class="xuanke">
        <div class="banner">
            <img src="imgs/xuanke/banner02.png" alt="">
        </div>
        <div class="solve_problem">
            <div class="inner">
                <div class="title">解决以下常见问题</div>
                <div class="title_box">
                    <p class="school">学校</p>
                    <p class="student">学生</p>
                </div>
                <ul class="main_box">
                    <li>
                        <img src="./imgs/xuanke/icon_paike.png" alt="">
                        <p>解决学生选科问题的同时，怎样进行合理的走班排课</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <img src="./imgs/xuanke/icon_xuanke.png" alt="">
                        <p>众多选科组合，如何找到最适合的。</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <img src="./imgs/xuanke/icon_zhiye.png" alt="">
                        <p>怎样了解职业专业及院校的选科要求。</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <img src="./imgs/xuanke/icon_renshiziwo.png" alt="">
                        <p>如何全面的了解自己。</p>
                    </li>

                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="kexuexuanke">
            <div class="title">产品优势</div>
            <div class="inner">
                <ul class="main_box">
                    <li style="background: url(./imgs/xuanke/icon_shuju.png) no-repeat">
                        <div class="num">
                            <img src="./imgs/xuanke/icon_01.png" alt="">
                        </div>
                        <p class="main_title">准确的数据内容</p>
                        <p class="main_detail">大学专业选科要求查询，科目可报专业查询，专业库、院校库、职业库</p>
                    </li>
                    <li style="background: url(./imgs/xuanke/icon_ziwopinggu.png) no-repeat">
                        <div class="num">
                            <img src="./imgs/xuanke/icon_02.png" alt="">
                        </div>
                        <p class="main_title">专业的自我评估</p>
                        <p class="main_detail">科学的测量方法，常模样本大数据采集，兴趣倾向与职业类型模型，自主知识产权</p>
                    </li>
                    <li style="background: url(./imgs/xuanke/icon_kexuedejuecefangfa.png) no-repeat">
                        <div class="num">
                            <img src="./imgs/xuanke/icon_03.png" alt="">
                        </div>
                        <p class="main_title">科学的决策方法</p>
                        <p class="main_detail">6选3、7选3、3+2+1等，多种选科方式，学生个性化选科</p>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="gongnengjieshao">
            <div class="title">功能介绍</div>
            <div class="inner">
                <div class="left main_box">
                    <div class="title_box">
                        360°选科
                    </div>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            <img src="./imgs/xuanke/icon_quanfangweiceping.png" alt="">
                            <p>经过全方位的测评和多维考量，提供科学选科方案</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <img src="./imgs/xuanke/icon_360xuanke02.png" alt="">
                            <p>包含生涯测评、目标专业选科要求查询、决策平衡单、生成选科结果功能</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="title_box">
                        专业科目要求查询
                    </div>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            <img src="./imgs/xuanke/icon_zhuanyekemuyaoqiuchaxun.png" alt="">
                            <p>根据自己的所选专业，快速查询院校专业的选科要求。</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="middle">
                    <img src="./imgs/xuanke/jieshao.png" alt="">
                </div>
                <div class="right main_box">
                    <div class="title_box">
                        根据专业选科目
                    </div>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            <img src="./imgs/xuanke/icon_genjuzhuanyexuankemu01.png" alt="">
                            <p>针对已测评学生，提供科学选科方案</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <img src="./imgs/xuanke/icon_genjuzhuanyexuankemu02.png" alt="">
                            <p>包含目标专业选科要求查询、决策平衡单、生成选科结果功能</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="title_box">
                        科目可报专业查询
                    </div>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            <img src="./imgs/xuanke/icon_kemukebaozhuanyechaxun.png" alt="">
                            <p>根据选考科目，学生可查询符合选科的高校和专业情况，以供学生在选科时做参考。</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="fuwuliucheng">
            <div class="title">服务流程</div>
            <div class="inner">
                <ul class="main_box">
                    <li>
                        <p class="main_title">专业与职业定位</p>
                        <p class="mian_detail">结合测评结果和考生实际情况，定位学生的专业和职业范围</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p class="main_title">外部探索</p>
                        <p class="mian_detail">根据学生的专业和职业范围，对标高校的选科要求</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p class="main_title">决策平衡</p>
                        <p class="mian_detail">指导学生使用决策平衡单，辅助进行选科方案的定量决策</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p class="main_title">选科决策</p>
                        <p class="mian_detail">指导学生在多种选科组合中，结合中学的选科资源，筛选出自己的选科组合</p>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="publicFoot"></div>
</body>
<script src="js/jquery-3.5.1.min.js"></script>
<script src="js/public.js"></script>
</html>
